# Goofre ACO — Code Ownership Rules
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default: core maintainers review everything
*                           @goofre-opensource/core-maintainers

# Core engine — strictest review
packages/core-engine/       @goofre-opensource/core-maintainers
packages/interfaces/        @goofre-opensource/core-maintainers

# Plugin SDK — plugin maintainers can also review
packages/plugins/           @goofre-opensource/core-maintainers @goofre-opensource/plugin-maintainers
packages/create-goofre-ucp/ @goofre-opensource/core-maintainers @goofre-opensource/plugin-maintainers
templates/                  @goofre-opensource/plugin-maintainers

# CI/CD and infrastructure — only core maintainers
.github/                    @goofre-opensource/core-maintainers
docker-compose.yml          @goofre-opensource/core-maintainers
turbo.json                  @goofre-opensource/core-maintainers

# Documentation — broader access
docs/                       @goofre-opensource/core-maintainers @goofre-opensource/plugin-maintainers
*.md                        @goofre-opensource/core-maintainers
